{"tid":1210593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警袋至少兩萬幾銀一個月 你服唔服？","createTime":"2019-06-12T14:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T17:05:22.000Z","uid":81398,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"501dab743e33853c46928d1163d3ad8a48b9ea23","tid":1210593,"uid":81398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190612/large/1560332190_15a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190612%2Flarge%2F1560332190_15a3.jpg&h=1eeaf1c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員準備出動前，於立法會內「大合照」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190612/large/1560333274_c8f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190612%2Flarge%2F1560333274_c8f9.jpg&h=8a50ab6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有示威者被催淚彈擊中，頭部重創，血流披面不斷吐血。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190612/large/1560332080_6918.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190612%2Flarge%2F1560332080_6918.jpg&h=26216374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有外籍人士被「清場」警員無故顏射胡椒噴劑多次，即使其同袍上前阻止亦無效。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/320563415521777/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F320563415521777%2F&h=7dc275e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網上影片拍到，數名防暴警察衝向一名落單的示威者，將其拉倒，其他同僚亦蜂擁而上，多人一同毆打該示威者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkpeanuts/videos/508913512981322/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkpeanuts%2Fvideos%2F508913512981322%2F&h=c3942259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員把夏𢡱道示威者驅趕到金鐘地鐵站口內之後，疑因不堪被罵黑警，失控至用胡椒噴霧射向手無寸鐵示威者，不理樓梯人多危險。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/video/20190612/480pix/1560333201_5301.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fvideo%2F20190612%2F480pix%2F1560333201_5301.png&h=c84fee74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警施放催淚彈後 拍手慶功：「呢個係你們嘅榮耀！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_675378_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_675378_0&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2yyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=4aa7d2aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_675378_0&h=3be792bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_675378_0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2dHq7gK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2dHq7gK.png&h=63c86bbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑警袋至少兩萬幾銀一個月 仲高過消防救護<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你服唔服？ 唔服就爭取扣佢地人工<br />\n香港人出份糧俾你嚟打香港人架？<br />\n唔扣佢哋人工等佢哋以為自己打香港人真係榮耀<br />\n呢班黑警傷天害理 滅絕人性<br />\n滿手鮮血 不知羞恥<br />\n豬狗不如 叫警犬都影衰啲狗<br />\n無能警 絕子絕孫 小心收尾嗰幾年<br />\n<br />\n以下開放一人一句 接力鬧爆黑警<br />\n榮耀？ 等佢哋行出街都抬唔起頭做豬狗不如</span></span>"},{"pid":"40207e677fd95413aeb0be6ac4a19ab3e88eb1bf","tid":1210593,"uid":56147,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:06:24.000Z","msg":"完全唔明要4萬個警察做乜     平時搵佢 唔係死人強姦關權貴事 又唔會理你"},{"pid":"246512ede38bb858c45c5dffcbb30d904f8ecd6f","tid":1210593,"uid":15880,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:09:22.000Z","msg":"屌你老母, 兩蚊都唔服"},{"pid":"a54dacc0b1954991465dc95c533f21e2ef88a278","tid":1210593,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:11:23.000Z","msg":"督察4萬5 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b392db0dcd7f408d6d8f56550ed8aab5899fe8","tid":1210593,"uid":189417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:12:43.000Z","msg":"還富於民啦"},{"pid":"5c962d6a69e28959d21eb13770c1eb429f52a9a2","tid":1210593,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":30,"score"